Package com.ibm.team.interop.common

Interface Summary
IExternalProxy Class to represent a proxy for an external object that is being replicated in the Jazz repository, and possibly synchronized with a Jazz item.
IExternalProxyHandle Represents a handle to an Item proxy.
IExternalRepositoryConnection Represents a connection to an external repository.
IExternalRepositoryConnectionHandle Comment for IExternalRepositoryConnectionHandle
IExternalState Class to represent the replicated state associated with a proxy for an external object.
IExternalStateHandle A handle for an IExternalState item.
IPropertyMapping Class to represent the identification of a property of an external object that is being replicated in a Jazz repository, and possibly synchronized with a property of a Jazz item.
ISyncRule A synchronization rule defines how external object properties and Jazz item properties are transformed into each other.
ISyncRuleHandle Handle for an ISyncRule item.
IValueMapping Class to represent an enumerated value mapping for a synchronized property.
 

Class Summary
IExternalProxy.SynchronizationDirection Possible values for the LAST_SYNC_DIRECTION property.
IExternalProxy.SynchronizationStatus Possible values for the SYNC_STATUS_PROPERTY.
InteropFactory Factory class for creating various Interop component objects in memory.
